collections.name: Invisible Struggles
collections.description:
"Invisible Struggles" is a deeply personal NFT collection that visualizes the silent battles of social anxiety, isolation, and self-doubt. Each piece represents the hidden weight carried by those who struggle daily, facing fears that others never see and fighting battles that remain unnoticed.

Through a blend of surreal and cyberpunk aesthetics, this collection tells the untold story of resilience in the face of internal struggles. Every artwork captures a different moment in the journey, whether it’s the weight of fear, the paralysis of doubt, or the masks worn to survive social interactions.

This collection is more than just art. It’s an expression of the unseen, a voice for the voiceless, and a reminder that even when no one sees the battle, the fight is real.

For those who understand, for those who relate, this is for you.

collections.name: Meta Genesis
collections.description:
Meta Genesis е футуристична NFT колекция, представяща кибернетични същества, AI интелекти и дигитални аватари от една алтернативна метавселена. Вдъхновена от киберпънк естетиката, неоновите технологии и квантовите реалности, тази колекция символизира началото на нова ера в дигиталното изкуство и изкуствения интелект.
Всеки NFT в колекцията е уникален, проектиран с внимателно изработени детайли като:
⚡ Неонови кибернетични импланти
⚡ Холографични елементи и цифрови мрежи
⚡ Футуристични AI създания, програмирани за метавселената
⚡ Дигитални аватари с адаптивен характер и специални способности
Светът на Meta Genesis е място, където изкуственият интелект еволюира отвъд познатите граници, превръщайки се в самостоятелна форма на съществуване.
Защо да станеш част от Meta Genesis?
Уникални дигитални идентичности – Всеки NFT е едно по рода си.
Част от ексклузивна метавселена – Притежателите на NFT ще имат достъп до бъдещи проекти, виртуални среди и специални колекционерски награди.

collections.name: The righteous king of the world
The righteous king of the world
Losing Oneself
collections.description:
Losing Oneself is series of generative NFT’s and corresponding plotter-drawings developed specifically for Cure³. Through a set of algorithmically generated psycho-geographic maps, the series explores the tension between the chaotic nature of reality and our simultaneous grasping for control. We plan out our lives, weaving intricate, fictitious structures that we try to inhabit, only to get repeatedly blindsided by chance, disorder, degeneration and eventual disintegration.

Drawing on inspiration from scientific diagrams, urban plans and neuronal mappings, the underlying algorithm produces a set of 128 visual poems. All the available iterations have been hand-picked by the artist from a set of more than 6.000 randomly generated seeds.

Token holders can order a corresponding pen plot for an additional fee equivalent to the mint price (more information to follow)

This project is part of the digital section of Cure³ at Bonhams, curated by Alex Estorick and Foteini Valeonti of reGEN.

collections.name: Veil of Horns
collections.description:
Veil of Horns is a captivating NFT collection that merges the enchanting allure of feminine beauty with the mystical strength of horns. Each piece in the collection features mesmerizing portraits of women adorned with stunning horns, symbolizing a unique blend of power, grace, and mysticism. With intricate details and a surreal, otherworldly aesthetic, these ethereal beings represent a journey through self-discovery, embracing both the softness and strength that reside within.

The Veil of Horns collection invites you to explore a world where beauty and power coexist in harmony, each piece a reflection of untamed femininity and mystery. As you immerse yourself in these beautifully crafted artworks, you’ll find yourself drawn into a realm where the veil between the earthly and the divine is thin, and the horns represent a connection to something greater.

Own a piece of this ethereal journey and let the Veil of Horns guide you into a universe filled with otherworldly beauty and strength

collections.name: Laughing Comedians
collections.description:
This NFT collection parodies Maurizio Cattelan’s Comedian, humorously reimagining the iconic work through cinematic scenes of women in minimalist attire. By compounding the original’s minimalism, this independent collection critiques the original's eccentricity, sparking a narrative about art's evolving nature in the digital age.

Unlike the original’s static composition, these dynamic and playful visuals offer distinct experiences—perfect to collect in a set or share with others who appreciate bold artistic expression and exclusivity. This transformative parody is unaffiliated with Maurizio Cattelan, Comedian, or its rights holders.
